

Broadcast - send to several IP addresses
1) 255.255.255.255 - broadcast. Send to this IP and message will get to everyone. INADDR_BROADCAST
Local area network broadcast

2) for example: 192.168.1.0 / 24 - first 24 bytes are unchanged.
				0.0.0.255
				OR

				brd 192.168.1.255 - отсылает и выше тоже по роутерам.

3) INADDR_LOOPBACK - адрес самого себя, общаются между собой но
через протоколы интернета.
4) broadcast - inform all
multicast - inform some
unicast - 

